{
  "stem": "11274.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he whistled a tune until he-- till he was tired of whistling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He danced with me, I think it was English Waltz, or was the-- the-- the Blue Danube waltz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Was it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he said, thank you, thank you, Miss Rena, That was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I said, well, thank you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I just have to say something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they didn't shake hands with anybody, no parents, not me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then they said, thank you very much, and they left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While I was standing there in front of with my father-- this had to be told because-- I-- I heard some voices, and I was terrified.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Their guns were already-- already pointed at us, two guns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Both officers didn't think it's enough one, but both of them, those soldiers, I mean.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was some kind of officer, I don't know the ranks really good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in that moment there, I wasn't looking for it, and I wasn't interested.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All I wanted is to do something for my father, if I could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I said, oh, I'm really losing my mind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I heard voices from a distance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And about two minutes later, I see two bikes, two high ranking officers on bikes, coming.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I-- these I knew their ranking because they had some medals and things like this on them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I recognized that was Hans Joksch was the name-- the-- the Austrian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was from Austria, he told me, too-- I'm from Vienna, Austria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know if he wanted to impress me, or something, but he told me that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the other one, he didn't tell me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And both of them were coming, Hans Joksch and his buddy, are coming by bikes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They stopped the bike, they took one look there and saw me and my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
